/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ringo-starr-cancels-autumn-tour-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ringo-starr-cancels-autumn-tour-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ringo-starr-cancels-autumn-tour-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔 (Ringo Starr)</a>因病缩短了 2024 年秋季美国巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-beatles-get-back-review-3103706">《披头士乐队：归来》评论：彼得·杰克逊漫长而曲折但绝对不容错过的史诗</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>鼓手计划于周二（9 月 24 日）和周三（25 日）在纽约市无线电城音乐厅在费城 The Mann 的 TD Pavilion 表演。</p><p>这位音乐家的代表在网上分享道：“林戈患了感冒，在咨询医生后，医生建议他取消剩下的两场演出并休息。”</p><p>持票人将通过电子邮件收到取消通知，并将在购买时退款。</p><p>社交媒体上的一篇帖子总结道：“一如既往，林戈和全明星队向粉丝们送去和平与爱，并希望很快能见到他们。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DATzzoaJzg7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" v